Introduction

This software provides a web interface and some scripts to deploy a SGE cluster on Open Nebula

Run:
ruby -rubygems xgrid.rb

Dependencies

apt-get install sqlite3 libsqlite3-dev build-essentials  libsinatra-ruby
gem install dm-core dm-sqlite-adapter dm-migrations amazon-ec2

Configuration

in xgrid.rb:
set :password, 'admin'  # Default admin password, TO BE MODIFIED
set :baseurl, ''  # Base URL of the service if not http://xxxx/

